main event: A UFO report involving a small, dark circular object observed in the sky at Holloman AFB, New Mexico on August 4, 1952.
interesting points: The report contains 7 photographs related to the sighting., The photographs depict various sky conditions with dark objects visible., Some images show silhouettes of trees and other structures against the sky., The photographs are largely black and white and appear to be old and damaged., There is no visible text provided in any of the photographs.
sighted object: small dark circular object in the sky
witness description: No witnesses confirmed in the report.
